AddressInfo.Title: Burlington NC Supercharger
AddressInfo.AccessComments: From I-85 Westbound:  Take exit 140 for University Dr toward Elon;  Turn right onto University Dr;  Turn right onto Boone Station Dr;  Turn left onto Glidewell Dr;  Turn right onto Boston Dr (at the parking lot);  Follow Boston Dr and turn right at the Kohl's;  Turn left down the first row of parking by the movie theater.  /   From I-85 Eastbound:  Take exit 140 for University Dr toward Elon;  Turn left onto University Dr;  Turn right onto Boone Station Dr;  Turn left onto Glidewell Dr; Turn right onto Boston Dr (at the parking lot); Follow Boston Dr and turn right at the Kohl's; Turn left down the first row of parking by the movie theater.
